Package: domogik-extras-dep
Architecture: all
Depends: domogik-common (= ${source:Version}), python-apscheduler,
 python-pyephem | python-ephem, python-bluez, python-mechanize,
 python-gdata
Description: Extra depencies for domogik.
 Domogik/Domoweb is a free home automation solution.
 It is based on the xPL protocol in order to easily use a lot of
 different technologies. Domogik is multi hosts and modulable.
 You can use as many user interfaces you want (actually there are two
 user interfaces : the web one and the Android one).
 This package is optional, it contains dependencies to python modules
 needed by some plugins :
  cron, dawndusk, bluez, sms, gagenda

Package: domogik-apache2
Architecture: all
Depends: apache2, libapache2-mod-proxy-html, libapache2-mod-auth-mysql
Description: Apache installation files for domogik.
 Domogik/Domoweb is a free home automation solution.
 It is based on the xPL protocol in order to easily use a lot of
 different technologies. Domogik is multi hosts and modulable.
 You can use as many user interfaces you want (actually there are two
 user interfaces : the web one and the Android one).
 This is the apache configuration for the Domogik rest server.
